title: Lodger - Low Blue Flame
description:

Bit Rate: 160kbps

(Ogg format is available, but you have to get it from their site)


Lodger put this album up on their website, Lodger.fi, on Christmas of 2013. 

It's not available for purchase yet, but keep an eye on their site in case this changes. This band deserves to be paid for what they do, because what they do is fantastic.
